=============
Release Notes
=============

--------------------------
Release v1.16.0 2020-02-27
--------------------------

New features
------------
- Added fingerprint detection for iOS to identify devices

Enhancements
------------
- Added "One Euro" filtering for joints.

Bug Fixes
------------
- None

Breaking changes
------------
- Head rotations now being done with quaternions.

--------------------------

--------------------------
Release v1.14.0 2019-10-08
--------------------------

New features
------------
- The Unity plugin has been updated to support 2018.4 LTS.
- Facial landmarks are now exposed in the Unity plugin.
- CPU-only version of wrnchAI is now compatible with Unity on windows.

Breaking changes
----------------

- The Unity plugin is not compatible with 2017.4 anymore.

--------------------------